<p>By adding class_weight='balanced', the Logistic Regression model's overall accuracy dropped to 63.92%. However, this is a more realistic and useful result because the model is now attempting to correctly classify both classes. The key improvement is in the recall for the diabetic class (from 0% to 64%), meaning it can now identify a substantial portion of actual diabetic patients.</p>
